---
const data = {
  title: 'A ZINE is a blueprint for culture.',
  items: [
    {
      q: '📚 Why ZINE?',
      a: [
        'A ZINE is not a vessel for displaying a finished work.',
        'It is a format for preserving the structure of trial and error as it is.',
        'Behind every work lies countless choices and decisions.',
        'ZINE was chosen to record them without omission.',
      ],
    },
    {
      q: '🧪 Why reveal the experimental process?',
      a: [
        'The goal is not transparency.',
        'It is to pass on a reproducible “method.”',
        'Thought, techniques, and criteria for decisions. By making the backbone of creation visible, readers can move from reading to creating.',
      ],
    },
    {
      q: '🌎 Why an English edition?',
      a: [
        'Culture stops the moment it closes itself.',
        'The English edition is not merely a translation.',
        'It is a mechanism that connects the culture outward.',
        'By crossing languages, the structure becomes universal.',
      ],
    },
  ],
};
---

<section id="about-zine" class="scroll-mt-16 relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-950 text-neutral-100">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-950 via-neutral-950/90 to-slate-950">
  </div>

  <div class="relative container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4">
    <header class="text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">{data.title}</h2>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-6 h-px w-20 bg-white/15"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="mt-10 md:mt-14 grid gap-6 md:gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      {
        data.items.map((it) => (
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 md:p-7 backdrop-blur">
            <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide">{it.q}</h3>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-200">
              {it.a.map((line) => (
                <p class="text-neutral-200/95">{line}</p>
              ))}
            </div>
          </article>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
